################################################################################
# Readme to work with translations.                                            #
################################################################################

Introduction
------------
Try to keep the default order. If there are no new strings in the GUI php files
you can jump to point 3.


Default order
-------------

1. makemsgs
	Use the shell script "makemsgs" to get all strings from GUI php files within
	the ispcp.pot file

2. updateToPot
	Use the shell script "updateToPot" to merge automatically the new (see
	point 1.) ispcp.pot file with the language specific *.po files.

3. modify *.po files
	Add translations for empty strings or fix wrong translations in the language
	specific *.po files.

4. create language text files
	Create/export language specific (.ini-like) text files with a language tool
	out of language specific *.po files. These text files can be used to upload
	them to the ispCP GUI panel.
